          <history-note id="DLM327686"><amended-provision>Section 2(1)</amended-provision><emphasis style="bold">proceeds</emphasis>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 May 2002</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM91082">section 3</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Receiverships Amendment Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 24).</history-note>
